data.description: Welcome to the Lennar at Plumas Lake community! This home was built in 2020 and it shows like a new home. Complete with RV access/storage, owned solar, new light fixtures and fans. Located on a huge corner lot, over 1/3 of an acre! This home has been meticulously well kept and maintained! Located close to highway access, parks, schools and shopping is only 11 mins away! Do not miss out on this opportunity to own a great home in a great location!
